						</button>
						<div class="faq-answer">
							<p>Everdantia is a magical digital forest where NFT art meets real-world conservation. Each tree in our collection represents both a unique piece of digital art and a commitment to protecting and restoring actual forests.</p>
							<p>We're building a living world where imagination and environmental action grow together. Every NFT purchase supports reforestation projects and conservation efforts worldwide.</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="faq-item">
