							<span class="faq-icon">üìÖ</span>
						</button>
						<div class="faq-answer">
							<p>We're currently in our growth phase, preparing for the Genesis Collection launch. While we don't have an official mint date yet, we're working hard to ensure everything is perfect for our community.</p>
							<p>Join our <a href={socialLinks.discord} target="_blank">Discord</a> and follow our <a href="/blog">blog</a> for the latest updates and early access opportunities!</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="faq-item">
						<button class="faq-question">
							How much will Everdantia NFTs cost?
							<span class="faq-icon">üí∞</span>
						</button>
						<div class="faq-answer">
							<p>Pricing details for the Genesis Collection will be announced closer to launch. We're committed to making our trees accessible while ensuring meaningful support for conservation efforts.</p>
							<p>Stay tuned to our community channels for pricing announcements and potential early supporter benefits.</p>
