							What makes Everdantia different from other NFT projects?
							<span class="faq-icon">‚ú®</span>
						</button>
						<div class="faq-answer">
							<p>Everdantia bridges the digital and natural worlds. Unlike typical NFT projects, we commit a significant portion of proceeds directly to real-world reforestation and conservation efforts.</p>
							<p>Our trees aren't just digital art‚Äîthey're seeds of change that grow into actual forests. Plus, our rich lore and worldbuilding create an immersive experience that goes beyond simple collectibles.</p>
