							Will there be different rarity levels?
							<span class="faq-icon">üíé</span>
						</button>
						<div class="faq-answer">
							<p>Yes! Our trees will have different rarity levels based on trunk types, leaf colors, domains, and special attributes. From common Oak to legendary Mystic Elder, each rarity tells a different story.</p>
							<p>Rarity affects not just visual appearance but also the lore and significance within the Everdantia world.</p>
						</div>
					</div>

