							<span class="faq-icon">üåø</span>
						</button>
						<div class="faq-answer">
							<p>Join our vibrant community on <a href={socialLinks.discord} target="_blank">Discord</a> where forest guardians share stories, discuss conservation, and get early updates.</p>
							<p>Follow us on <a href={socialLinks.twitter} target="_blank">Twitter</a> and <a href={socialLinks.instagram} target="_blank">Instagram</a> for visual updates and announcements.</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="faq-item">
						<button class="faq-question">
